#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.5.0/lua-api/net.md:1
msgid "Network API"
msgstr "ネットワーク API"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.5.0/lua-api/net.md:3
msgid ""
"URL, IP, and host/port parsing helpers are available under `ptool.net` and "
"`p.net`."
msgstr "URL、IP、host/port 解析ヘルパーは `ptool.net` と `p.net` にあります。"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.5.0/lua-api/net.md:5
msgid "ptool.net.parse_url"
msgstr "ptool.net.parse_url"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.5.0/lua-api/net.md:7
msgctxt "/Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.5.0/lua-api/net.md:7"
msgid "`v0.2.0` - Introduced."
msgstr "`v0.2.0` - Introduced."

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.5.0/lua-api/net.md:9
msgid ""
"`ptool.net.parse_url(input)` parses a URL string and returns a normalized "
"parts table."
msgstr "`ptool.net.parse_url(input)` は URL 文字列を解析し、正規化された各部の テーブ"
"ルを返します。"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.5.0/lua-api/net.md:12
msgctxt "/Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.5.0/lua-api/net.md:12"
msgid "Arguments:"
msgstr "引数:"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.5.0/lua-api/net.md:14
msgid "`input` (string, required): The URL to parse."
msgstr "`input` (string, 必須): 解析する URL。"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.5.0/lua-api/net.md:16
msgctxt "/Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.5.0/lua-api/net.md:16"
msgid "Returns: A table with the following fields:"
msgstr "戻り値: 次のフィールドを持つテーブル。"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.5.0/lua-api/net.md:18
msgid "`kind` (string): Always `\"url\"`."
msgstr "`kind` (string): 常に `\"url\"`。"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.5.0/lua-api/net.md:19
msgctxt "/Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.5.0/lua-api/net.md:19"
msgid "`input` (string): The original input string."
msgstr "`input` (string): 元の入力文字列。"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.5.0/lua-api/net.md:20
msgid "`normalized` (string): The normalized URL string."
msgstr "`normalized` (string): 正規化された URL 文字列。"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.5.0/lua-api/net.md:21
msgid "`scheme` (string): The URL scheme."
msgstr "`scheme` (string): URL スキーム。"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.5.0/lua-api/net.md:22
msgid "`username` (string, optional): The decoded username, if present."
msgstr "`username` (string, 任意): 存在する場合のデコード済みユーザー名。"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.5.0/lua-api/net.md:23
msgid "`password` (string, optional): The decoded password, if present."
msgstr "`password` (string, 任意): 存在する場合のデコード済みパスワード。"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.5.0/lua-api/net.md:24
msgid "`host` (string, optional): The hostname or IP literal, if present."
msgstr "`host` (string, 任意): 存在する場合のホスト名または IP リテラル。"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.5.0/lua-api/net.md:25
msgid ""
"`host_kind` (`\"domain\"|\"ipv4\"|\"ipv6\"`, optional): The host "
"classification, if a host is present."
msgstr "`host_kind` (`\"domain\"|\"ipv4\"|\"ipv6\"`, 任意): ホストが存在する場合の ホ"
"スト分類。"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.5.0/lua-api/net.md:27
msgid "`port` (integer, optional): The explicit port, if present."
msgstr "`port` (integer, 任意): 存在する場合の明示的なポート。"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.5.0/lua-api/net.md:28
msgid "`path` (string): The URL path."
msgstr "`path` (string): URL パス。"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.5.0/lua-api/net.md:29
msgid "`query` (string, optional): The query string without the leading `?`."
msgstr "`query` (string, 任意): 先頭の `?` を含まないクエリ文字列。"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.5.0/lua-api/net.md:30
msgid "`fragment` (string, optional): The fragment without the leading `#`."
msgstr "`fragment` (string, 任意): 先頭の `#` を含まないフラグメント。"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.5.0/lua-api/net.md:43
msgid "ptool.net.parse_ip"
msgstr "ptool.net.parse_ip"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.5.0/lua-api/net.md:45
msgctxt "/Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.5.0/lua-api/net.md:45"
msgid "`v0.2.0` - Introduced."
msgstr "`v0.2.0` - Introduced."

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.5.0/lua-api/net.md:47
msgid ""
"`ptool.net.parse_ip(input)` parses an IPv4 or IPv6 address and returns a "
"normalized parts table."
msgstr ""
"`ptool.net.parse_ip(input)` は IPv4 または IPv6 アドレスを解析し、 正規化され"
"た各部のテーブルを返します。"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.5.0/lua-api/net.md:50
msgctxt "/Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.5.0/lua-api/net.md:50"
msgid "Arguments:"
msgstr "引数:"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.5.0/lua-api/net.md:52
msgid "`input` (string, required): The IP address to parse."
msgstr "`input` (string, 必須): 解析する IP アドレス。"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.5.0/lua-api/net.md:54
msgctxt "/Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.5.0/lua-api/net.md:54"
msgid "Returns: A table with the following fields:"
msgstr "戻り値: 次のフィールドを持つテーブル。"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.5.0/lua-api/net.md:56
msgid "`kind` (string): Always `\"ip\"`."
msgstr "`kind` (string): 常に `\"ip\"`。"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.5.0/lua-api/net.md:57
msgctxt "/Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.5.0/lua-api/net.md:57"
msgid "`input` (string): The original input string."
msgstr "`input` (string): 元の入力文字列。"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.5.0/lua-api/net.md:58
msgid "`normalized` (string): The normalized IP address."
msgstr "`normalized` (string): 正規化された IP アドレス。"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.5.0/lua-api/net.md:59
msgid "`version` (integer): `4` for IPv4 or `6` for IPv6."
msgstr "`version` (integer): IPv4 の場合は `4`、IPv6 の場合は `6`。"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.5.0/lua-api/net.md:68
msgid "ptool.net.parse_host_port"
msgstr "ptool.net.parse_host_port"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.5.0/lua-api/net.md:70
msgctxt "/Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.5.0/lua-api/net.md:70"
msgid "`v0.2.0` - Introduced."
msgstr "`v0.2.0` - Introduced."

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.5.0/lua-api/net.md:72
msgid ""
"`ptool.net.parse_host_port(input)` parses a `host:port` string and returns a "
"normalized parts table."
msgstr ""
"`ptool.net.parse_host_port(input)` は `host:port` 文字列を解析し、 正規化され"
"た各部のテーブルを返します。"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.5.0/lua-api/net.md:75
msgctxt "/Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.5.0/lua-api/net.md:75"
msgid "Arguments:"
msgstr "引数:"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.5.0/lua-api/net.md:77
msgid ""
"`input` (string, required): The host and port string. IPv6 addresses must "
"use bracket notation such as `[2001:db8::1]:443`."
msgstr ""
"`input` (string, 必須): ホストとポートの文字列。IPv6 アドレスは `"
"[2001:db8::1]:443` のように角括弧表記を使う必要があります。"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.5.0/lua-api/net.md:80
msgctxt "/Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.5.0/lua-api/net.md:80"
msgid "Returns: A table with the following fields:"
msgstr "戻り値: 次のフィールドを持つテーブル。"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.5.0/lua-api/net.md:82
msgid "`kind` (string): Always `\"host_port\"`."
msgstr "`kind` (string): 常に `\"host_port\"`。"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.5.0/lua-api/net.md:83
msgctxt "/Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.5.0/lua-api/net.md:83"
msgid "`input` (string): The original input string."
msgstr "`input` (string): 元の入力文字列。"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.5.0/lua-api/net.md:84
msgid "`normalized` (string): The normalized `host:port` string."
msgstr "`normalized` (string): 正規化された `host:port` 文字列。"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.5.0/lua-api/net.md:85
msgid "`host` (string): The normalized host value."
msgstr "`host` (string): 正規化された host 値。"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.5.0/lua-api/net.md:86
msgid "`host_kind` (`\"domain\"|\"ipv4\"|\"ipv6\"`): The host classification."
msgstr "`host_kind` (`\"domain\"|\"ipv4\"|\"ipv6\"`): ホスト分類。"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.5.0/lua-api/net.md:87
msgid "`port` (integer): The parsed port."
msgstr "`port` (integer): 解析されたポート。"
